def isrotation(x, y):
  temp=x
  leng=len(str(x))
  if(x==y):
    return True
  s=list(str(x))
  l=list(str(y))
  # print(s[-1::-1])
  # print(l)
  if(s[-1::-1]==l):
    return True
  for i in range(leng+1):
    r=x%10
    q=x//10
    x=10**(leng-1)*r+q
    # x=rotate(x)
    if(x==y):
      return True
  return False
